	abstract = {Objective: Tractography has been used to define the presurgical location of white matter tracts, but this is subjective and time-intensive, making incorporation to imaging workflow at scale problematic. The objective is to validate a fully automated pipeline using the TractSeg algorithm (Wasserthal et al. NeuroImage 2018;183:239–253) to segment the corticospinal tract in patients with brain tumors adjacent to the corticospinal tract.
